headline: Walmart Is Retail King Again. Can It Keep the Crown?
summary: Walmart  a 62-year-old retailer, looks sharper than it has in a long time.  After years of lagging behind the retail stars  Costco Wholesale  and  Amazon.com  Walmart is catching up quickly.  Walmart has become an e-commerce heavyweight, and it is gaining share with both low- and high-income shoppers.
